Package: sharkabc3d
Title: Shark and Ray Abiotic Covariates in 3 Dimensions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jay", "Matsushiba", , "jay.matsushiba@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0496-9188"))
Description: Facilitates the analysis of shark and ray habitat in 3D, enabling
    descriptions of habitat by depth and area. Provides tools for volume
    calculation, environmental extraction, and spatial overlap analysis between
    species ranges, fisheries, and protected areas.
